OL,3,CHolidays 'top spending priority' for
OL,4,Chouseholds, survey finds
OL,6,FHolidays are households' top spending
OL,7,Fpriority when it comes to splashing
OL,8,Fdiscretionary cash, ahead of dining
OL,9,Fout and home renovations, a survey has
OL,10,Findicated.
OL,12,FAlthough many people have just settled
OL,13,Finto a "back-to-school" routine,
OL,14,Fanother holiday could be just around
OL,15,Fthe corner for some, the research
OL,16,Fsuggests.
