OL,3,CHolidays 'top spending priority' for
OL,4,Chouseholds, survey finds
OL,6,FNearly three-quarters (71%) of people
OL,7,Fsurveyed had taken a holiday in the
OL,8,Fpast 12 months.
OL,10,FAbout a third (34%) of holidaymakers
OL,11,Fsurveyed estimated they will spend
OL,12,Fmore on holidays this year than last,
OL,13,Fwith 56% planning to spend around the
OL,14,Fsame and 9% looking to cut back.
OL,16,FWhile people typically spent between
OL,17,F#501 and #1,000 on a single holiday
OL,18,Fbooking in the past year, those
OL,19,Fearning over #120,000 spent #9,501 to
OL,20,F#10,000 on a single trip.
