OL,3,CHolidays 'top spending priority' for
OL,4,Chouseholds, survey finds
OL,6,FThe research also found the most
OL,7,Fpopular holiday luxuries that people
OL,8,Fenjoy are local shopping and buying
OL,9,Fsouvenirs, luxury accommodation,
OL,10,Fdrinks at scenic venues or rooftop
OL,11,Fbars, and dining out at high-end or
OL,12,Ffamous restaurants.
OL,14,FSteve Byrne, chief executive officer
OL,15,Fof Travel Counsellors, said: "Our
OL,16,Flatest data shows people are not just
OL,17,Fdreaming about holidays ` they're
OL,18,Fplanning, saving and spending to make
OL,19,Fthem a reality.
